 in the dropdown to see credit redistribute instantly\\n3. Hit **Compare All** to see a side-by-side table of every model at once\\n4. The **prompt output** at the bottom generates a ready-to-copy question you can paste back into Claude for deeper analysis\\n\\n`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`\\n- The key takeaway from attribution is that **the same data tells completely different stories** depending on which model you choose. First Touch says \\\"Google Ads drives all our revenue,\\\" Last Touch says \\\"the Pricing Page does,\\\" and Linear says \\\"everyone helped equally.\\\" None is objectively correct — the right model depends on your sales cycle length and what decisions you're optimizing for.\\n- **U-Shaped is the most popular compromise** in practice because it acknowledges two critical moments (discovery + conversion) while still giving some credit to nurture steps. Time Decay is best when recency truly matters (e.g., flash sales).\\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":212,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":52693,\"output_tokens\":431,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":212,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYnEtZ31c5PU9HjWkqG44\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"728abff5-e241-4b02-bb8c-5184ecc77796\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-06T17:43:16.647Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"728abff5-e241-4b02-bb8c-5184ecc77796\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"6ce8c9a4-5500-40f6-a6c7-8746f1f799f4\",\"version\":\"2.1.70\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"slug\":\"cuddly-skipping-duckling\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"